# ChangeLog for <sys-apps>/<baselayout-admin>

  07 Nov 2007; Vincent Strubel <clipos@ssi.gouv.fr>
  Remove all ebuilds before 1.1.0.

*baselayout-admin-1.1.0 (16 Jul 2007)

  16 Jul 2007; Vincent Strubel <clipos@ssi.gouv.fr>
  +baselayout-admin-1.1.0.ebuild:
  Create a dedicated /etc tree by using the new views.eclass.

*baselayout-admin-1.0-r4 (25 Jun 2007)

  25 Jun 2007; Vincent Strubel <clipos@ssi.gouv.fr>
  +baselayout-admin-1.0-r4.ebuild:
  Remove stupid SRC_URI.

*baselayout-admin-1.0-r3 (27 Jul 2006)

  27 Jul 2006; Vincent Strubel <clipos@ssi.gouv.fr>
  +baselayout-admin-1.0-r3.ebuild:
  Removed device creation, which is now done in the core, since
  it needs CAP_MKNOD. See clip-layout/rm-devices.

*baselayout-admin-1.0-r2 (22 Jun 2006)

  22 Jun 2006; Vincent Strubel <clipos@ssi.gouv.fr>
  +baselayout-admin-1.0-r2.ebuild:
  Remove BSD ptys, which are no longer supported by clip-kernel.

*baselayout-admin-1.0-r1 (03 May 2006)

  03 May 2006; Vincent Strubel <clipos@ssi.gouv.fr>
  +baselayout-admin-1.0-r1.ebuild:
  Create a /usr/etc/ssh mountpoint for config files coming from 
  update_priv view.

*baselayout-admin-1.0 (08 apr 2006)

  08 Apr 2006; Vincent Strubel <clipos@ssi.gouv.fr>
  +baselayout-admin-1.0.ebuild:
  Initial import. 
